{"title":"linux+python+virtual environment","date":"2019-10-08T03:49:31.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Oct 8, 2019","L":"10/08/2019","MM-DD":"10-08"},"link":"2019/10/08/Linux+python+virtual environment","tags":["Linux","server"],"updated":"2020-03-17T15:56:57.793Z","content":"<p>通常实验室里一个服务器是大家公用的，为了不引起包冲突，创建一个虚拟环境是很有必要的。通常实验室里一个服务器是大家公用的，为了不引起包冲突，创建一个虚拟环境是很有必要的。</p>\n<h1 id=\"创建\">创建<a href=\"2019/10/08/Linux+python+virtual environment#创建\"></a></h1><p>步骤如下：</p>\n<p>我将用conda来创建</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>检查是否安装conda以及当前conda版本</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">conda -V</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n\n\n</li>\n</ol>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><p>查看当前已创建的虚拟环境有哪些</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">conda env list</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p> 或 </p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">conda info -e</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n\n\n</li>\n</ol>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><p>创建一个名为 env1 且python解析器为2.7版本的虚拟环境</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">conda create -n env1 python=2.7</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>由此，虚拟环境可在Anaconda安装目录envs文件夹下找到。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"使用\">使用<a href=\"2019/10/08/Linux+python+virtual environment#使用\"></a></h1><ol>\n<li><p>使用激活</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">source activate env1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n\n\n</li>\n</ol>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><p>给env1安装额外的包</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">conda install -n env1 [package]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>即可安装package到新创建的env1中。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>关闭环境</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">source deactivate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n\n\n</li>\n</ol>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li><p>移除虚拟环境</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>移除env1环境中的某个包</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">conda remove --name $env1 $package_name</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>移除某个虚拟环境</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">conda remove -n env1 --all</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n","prev":{"title":"GPU manual for the poor","link":"2019/10/08/GPU manual for the poor"},"next":{"title":"hexo's usage","link":"2019/10/08/hexo usage"},"plink":"https://thswind.github.io/2019/10/08/Linux+python+virtual environment/","toc":[{"title":"创建","id":"创建","index":"1"},{"title":"使用","id":"使用","index":"2"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"custom":"禁止转载-非商用-THSWind"}}